KY 22/Ballardsville Rd is blocked for a slide repair between the KY 22/KY 53 intersection in Oldham Co and mile point 0.35 (near Radcliff Rd) in Henry Co.  Motorists should follow the signed detours.  Drivers should continue on KY 22 (Ballardsville Road) to KY 53, then follow KY 322 (Lucas Road/McCoun Road) in Shelby and Henry Counties to reconnect with KY 22 beyond the closure.  Motorists traveling from Henry County to La Grange should take KY 1861 (Smithfield Road) to Radcliff Road, then continue on KY 712 (Jericho Road) to reach La Grange.  Local traffic should navigate around the closure via Ballard Vista Drive on the west side of the work zone or Ballard Glenn Parkway on the east side.
